sentence.text: Further, high activation of NF-kappaB-inducing kinase activity expression level was correlated with higher tumor stage, lymph node metastasis, myometrial invasion, and lower survival rate.

These collective data indicated that activation of NF-kappaB-inducing kinase activity overexpression promotes EC tumorigenesis by activating mitotic cell cycle and cell division pathways, and IRAK1 may serve as a promising therapeutic strategy for EC
